FBIS4-36379 "drnes110dd_94019" FBIS-NES-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 Palestinian Affairs Shin Bet Uncovers Attempt To Assassinate Al-Rujub Shin Bet Uncovers Attempt To Assassinate Al-Rujub TA0706181794 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in Hebrew 1700 GMT 7 Jun 94 TA0706181794 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network Hebrew BFN [Text] The Shin Bet several days ago uncovered an assassination attempt against Jibril al-Rujub, head of the Palestinian preventive security service. Al-Rujub, who was in Tulkarm that day, was informed he had better cancel a planned visit to Nabulus because he can expect an unpleasant surprise there. The tension between the Palestinian police and Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] in the Gaza and Jericho autonomy areas is increasing.
